    {
      "id": "18e4750c-f3ba-8094-9022-ec5375a7f3ae",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Results show that peer capital and faculty capital contribute positively to study success. Moreover, high-achievers have a positive influence in low-achievers if they are friends.",
